                                 Welcome to the
               Center for Biologics Evaluation and Research (CBER)

     The Mission of the Center for Biologics Evaluation and Research (CBER)
   is to protect and enhance the public health through regulation of
   biological products including blood, vaccines, therapeutics and related
   drugs and devices according to statutory authorities. Our goal is to
   provide you with timely and relevant information about CBER's
   regulatory requirements and activities, and about the products we
   regulate.
